title: Trump continues to suck the air out of the GOP primary
description: There was a window when the Republican party looked like it was ready to move on, but the party is once again "reliving the worst" parts of the Trump presidency.

title: Republicans release top targets of Democratic-held House seats in 2024
description: The National Republican Congressional Committee is eyeing 37 seats next cycle in an attempt to expand the GOP's razor-thin majority.
